title: Lady of the Manor
description: Lady of the Manor is a 2021 American comedy film written and directed by brothers Justin Long and Christian Long in their directorial debuts. It stars Melanie Lynskey, Judy Greer, Justin Long, Ryan Phillippe, Luis Guzm\u00E1n, and Patrick Duffy. The film premiered at the opening night of the Gasparilla International Film Festival on June 10, 2021, and is due to be released by Lionsgate on September 17, 2021.

imdbInfo.ratingReason: Rated R for language throughout, sexual material and drug use
